<span id="freeTextContainer6770763887887296649">This was a re-read for me. I read it back in the late 70&apos;s when it first came out, and even then I didn&apos;t think it was that great. <br/>Now, I was compelled to finish, but if it weren&apos;t for Ray Porter&apos;s narration I might not have.<br/><br/>This isn&apos;t great writing, but the story is interesting as hell. All these years later I&apos;m still wondering how much of this actually happened.</span>
  <span id="freeText6770763887887296649" style="display:none">This was a re-read for me. I read it back in the late 70's when it first came out, and even then I didn't think it was that great. <br />Now, I was compelled to finish, but if it weren't for Ray Porter's narration I might not have.<br /><br />This isn't great writing, but the story is interesting as hell. All these years later I'm still wondering how much of this actually happened.</span>
