<div id="review_4281704789" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4281704789" />
    <a title="Morgan Stewart" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/117962894-morgan-stewart"><img alt="Morgan Stewart" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1600051071p2/117962894.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4281704789?book_show_action=true">Oct 13, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Morgan Stewart" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Morgan Stewart" href="/user/show/117962894-morgan-stewart">Morgan Stewart</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer4281704789&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4281704789" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer938909007416032400">Ok, ok I know this book is very polarizing for most. Knowing some of the backstory (and having never watched any of the movies), I read this book as if it were fiction. So that’s where I’m coming from. <br/><br/>I thought it was entertaining, well-paced, and not too scary. I was also mainly concerned for Harry throughout the book, so I’m glad he made it out mostly unscathed. <br/><br/>What can I say, because I read it as a “fiction”, I liked it!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

